{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01CfMcVuvcjNeuZdKFe5X61g","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the exploration, here's a comprehensive overview of the codebase:\n\n1. Directory Structure:\n   - Main package: `org.springframework.samples.petclinic`\n   - Subpackages: \n     - `model`: Base entity classes\n     - `owner`: Owner and Pet-related classes\n     - `vet`: Veterinarian-related classes\n     - `system`: System configurations and controllers\n\n2. Build System:\n   - Maven (pom.xml)\n   - Spring Boot version: 3.3.0\n   - Java Version: 17\n   - Build Plugins:\n     - Spring Boot Maven Plugin\n     - Checkstyle\n     - JaCoCo (code coverage)\n     - Native GraalVM support\n\n3. Key Dependencies:\n   - Spring Boot Starters:\n     - Web\n     - Data JPA\n     - Thymeleaf\n     - Actuator\n     - Validation\n   - Databases:\n     - H2 (default)\n     - MySQL\n     - PostgreSQL\n   - Caching: Caffeine\n   - Frontend: WebJars (Bootstrap, Font Awesome)\n\n4. Configuration:\n   - `application.properties`:\n     - Database: H2 by default\n     - Thymeleaf mode: HTML\n     - JPA configuration\n     - Internationalization\n     - Actuator endpoints exposed\n     - Logging configurations\n\n5. Main Application Class:\n   - `PetClinicApplication.java`\n   - Uses `@SpringBootApplication`\n   - Uses `@ImportRuntimeHints`\n\n6. Controllers:\n   - `WelcomeController`\n   - `VetController`\n   - `OwnerController`\n   - `PetController`\n   - `VisitController`\n   - `CrashController`\n\n7. Spring Annotations Used:\n   - `@Controller`\n   - `@Configuration`\n   - `@Bean`\n   - `@Component`\n   - `@Transactional`\n   - `@SpringBootApplication`\n\n8. Dockerfile Details:\n   - Base Image: maven:3.9.12-ibm-semeru-21-noble\n   - Includes Python and Playwright setup\n   - Copies project files\n   - Default CMD: `mvn clean spring-boot:run`\n\n9. Test Support:\n   - JUnit 5\n   - TestContainers\n   - MySQL and PostgreSQL Integration Tests\n   - Comprehensive unit and integration tests\n\n10. Additional Features:\n    - Internationalization (multiple language properties files)\n    - Custom CSS with SCSS support\n    - Database schema and data SQL scripts for multiple databases\n    - Static resources and templates\n\nKey Technologies:\n- Framework: Spring Boot 3.3.0\n- Java 17\n- JPA/Hibernate\n- Thymeleaf\n- Maven\n- Multiple Database Support\n\nThis is a comprehensive Spring Boot Pet Clinic application with modern Java and Spring ecosystem practices, supporting multiple databases and providing a full-featured web application for managing a veterinary clinic."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"989b6ec8-5330-484b-9e5f-c61fa819ffe2","uuid":"0b6fabc6-783d-4030-a169-4294796b274a"}
