{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VR1H3sFBQXmoWJGwcCpwJt","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now run the smoke tests. The test for `test_vets_json_api` sends an `Accept: */*` header by default with `requests`, but the VetResource's `/vets` endpoint is `@Produces(APPLICATION_JSON)` only - let me make sure it gets JSON properly. Let me also check if `test_owners_list` might fail because the search returns only 1 result (single owner redirects):\n\nActually, `test_owners_list` uses `lastName=\"\"` which matches all owners (10+), so it should show the list. Let me run the smoke tests:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":508,"cache_read_input_tokens":62316,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":508,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":288},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"989b6ec8-5330-484b-9e5f-c61fa819ffe2","uuid":"989cc3a1-939a-40e9-9c38-41b682403bbc"}
